f_b
f_b(x) = b^x
\lim_{b \rightarrow \infty} \lim_{h \rightarrow 0} \frac{b^h - 1}{h} = \lim_{b \rightarrow \infty} f_b'(0) = \lim_{b \rightarrow \infty} \log(b) = \infty
\lim_{h\to 0}\frac{b^h-1}h\stackrel{\text{l'Hospital}}=\lim_{h\to 0}b^h\log b=\log b
\lim_{b\to\infty}\log b=\infty
